---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Cookie Policy"
  description="Learn which essential and analytics cookies Unleft uses on unleft.space and how to manage them in your browser."
  keywords="Unleft cookie policy, analytics cookies, essential cookies, cookie preferences"
  imageAlt="Unleft cookie policy page preview"
  ogType="article"
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 px-4">
      <Badge className="mb-6 bg-accent-primary/10 text-accent-glow border-none mx-auto w-fit font-gupter">Legal & Safety</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 tracking-tighter">
        Cookie <span class="text-accent-primary">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Managing your digital footprint. How we use cookies to enhance your experience.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-mono text-accent-glow uppercase tracking-widest">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-accent-primary/5 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-[#2D2D44] bg-[#0A0A0F]/60 p-8 md:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-16 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help us provide a better browsing experience.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">2. What cookies we use</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <ul class="flex flex-col gap-5 list-disc pl-5 marker:text-accent-primary/60 text-base/loose">
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">Essential cookies</strong>: FormSubmit.co may set a functional cookie for spam protection. These are necessary for the contact form to work and do not track your browsing.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary font-medium">Analytics cookies</strong>: We use Google Analytics to understand website usage. These cookies collect anonymous data about page views and interactions. You can opt out via <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-glow hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent-primary/30">Google's Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">3. Managing cookies</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling essential cookies may break form functionality.</p>
          </div>
      
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="font-gupter text-2xl md:text-3xl text-text-primary tracking-wide">4. Contact</h2>
            <div class="bg-accent-primary/20 h-px w-12 rounded-full mb-2"></div>
            <p class="text-base/loose">For questions about our cookie practices, contact <a href="mailto:hello@unleft.space" class="text-accent-glow hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-accent-primary/30">hello@unleft.space</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
